{
    "name": "Drow Poisoner",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Before Combat</b> The poisoner drinks her Dexterity mutagen and her extracts of <i>anticipate peril</i>, <i>countless eyes</i>, and <i>greater invisibility</i>.<br/><b>Base Statistics</b> Without the Dexterity mutagen, <i>anticipate peril</i>, and <i>countless eyes</i>, the drow\u2019s statistics are <b>Init</b> +7; <b>Senses</b> no all-around vision; <b>AC</b> 21, touch 14, flat-footed 18; Ref +12, Will +6; <b>Ranged</b> mwk hand crossbow +13 (1d4/19\u201320 plus poison), or bomb +12/+7 (6d6+5 fire); <b>Dex</b> 17, <b>Wis</b> 12; <b>CMD</b> 23; <b>Skills</b> Disable Device +17, Fly +11, Heal +10, Perception +18, Stealth +14, Survival +10."
        },
        {
            "name": "Ecology",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> underground"
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "This drow makes use of deadly venoms and alchemy."
        }
    ],
